name: IndianapolisGuide
0:
”Alexa, open Indy guide”
”Alexa, ask Indy Guide to tell me the top five things to do”
”Alexa, Ask Indy Guide to tell me the news”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: indy guide
des: With the Indianapolis Guide skill, you can ask Alexa about the best attractions available in Indianapolis. It is a handy tool for locals or if you're just traveling through! To get started, open the guide and ask for the best places to visit for entertainment, food, or cultural experiences. Get stuck? Just say help and Alexa will help you find your way.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
